Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不困
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好久都没这么爽快了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗 那群人的表情！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,挺起胸膛 好不容易才卸下了伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我家往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,再过几个小时 大家就会看到那间教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伯也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那 今天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 今天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不困
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不能回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 我的「普通的人生」就会走到尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊高男 你已经起床了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是睡到快要迟到才起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,吓得我都要折寿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开始就要换夏季校服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈去帮你熨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,705)}你脑子有病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,705)}好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,705)}别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,705)}变态痴汉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,705)}消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,705)}别过来 会传染
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,705)}你打骨子里就烂掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,705)}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,705)}绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,705)}你这种人别来学校了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,春日 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,远走他乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,趁这个机会就这样远走他乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开始就要换夏季校服了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 跟你说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是内心舒坦多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再次正式地 今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,春日你怎么了 要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有点吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人 这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太惨了！教室被弄得乱七八糟了！你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了！那个变态又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴山田 别叽叽喳喳的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,给我考虑考虑奈奈子的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字 被墨汁盖掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都去体育馆 临时大会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,动作都快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,临时！临时！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈子 能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Comment: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B PART====================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天2年1班发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,教室被恶意破坏 教科书等学生私有物品被损毁的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,目前还没能了解到具体情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给我安静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}接下来会尽快着手现场和事件的确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你不觉得很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的学校居然发生了这种事诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你们几个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,电视台也要来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}给我安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啊 采访什么的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}各位同学也不要过于恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这果然是那个人干的吧 目击到的偷走佐伯体操服的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是啊 听说是个戴眼镜的死宅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}以校规为准则 做出符合高中生形象的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 我会不会被袭击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈子好可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}出于安全的考虑 今天开始大家要集体离校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,2年1班在几楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没暴露安心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,仲村…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好久都没这么爽快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗 那群人的表情！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,挺起胸膛 好不容易才卸下了伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 是「恶之花」封面上的画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个画到地板上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是春日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那间教室也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的体操服也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都是春日干的吧
